performing daily trivia and ultimately become enslaved by it.
     -- Gulf Maritime Corporation
%
Whatever you can do or dream you can do, begin it! Boldness has power,
magic and genius in it.
     -- Goethe
%
I do not believe that any man lives up to his ideals, but if we are
striving, if we are working, if we are trying, to the best of our
ability, to improve day by day, then we are in the line of our duty. If
we are seeking to remedy our own defects, if we are so living that we
can ask God for light, for knowledge, for intelligence, and above all,
for his spirit, that we may overcome our weaknesses, then, I can tell
you, we are in the straight and narrow path that leads to life eternal.
Then we need have no fear.
     -- Heber J. Grant
